<text><body>
<lb n="0190b15" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0190b16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0190b17" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 949</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0190b18" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0190039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】東寺三密藏古寫本，【甲】石山寺藏古寫本</note>奇特最勝金輪佛頂念誦儀軌法
<lb n="0190b19" ed="T"/>要</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0190b20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0190b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0190b2101">夫欲修習一字頂輪王法者。先須入大曼荼羅
<lb n="0190b22" ed="T"/>海會。從師親<note n="0190040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝授【甲】</note><note n="0190040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受【大】，授【甲】</note><app n="0190040"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">授</rdg></app>灌頂。既蒙印可方得諮。學微
<lb n="0190b23" ed="T"/>妙軌則真言教門。建立道場。一依本部儀式。
<lb n="0190b24" ed="T"/>畫本尊像。如法安置。若欲疾成悉地。先須沐
<lb n="0190b25" ed="T"/>浴。著新淨衣。若出家者。精持律儀。不得缺
<lb n="0190b26" ed="T"/>犯。若在家者。應受近住八支淨戒。復當殷重
<lb n="0190b27" ed="T"/>發廣大心。於阿闍梨所敬仰如佛。愍諸有情
<lb n="0190b28" ed="T"/>起大悲願。不惜身命常生濟度。悉令離苦獲
<lb n="0190b29" ed="T"/>大利樂。入道場已。五輪投地。虔誠<note n="0190041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">普＝並【甲】</note><note n="0190041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">普【大】，並【甲】</note><app n="0190041"><lem wit="【大】">普</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">並</rdg></app>禮一切
<pb n="0190c" xml:id="T19.0949.0190c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0190c01" ed="T"/>如來。復對本尊。恒沙聖眾以淨三業悔除罪
<lb n="0190c02" ed="T"/>障。勸請諸佛轉妙法輪。隨喜三乘所修福智。
<lb n="0190c03" ed="T"/>以斯妙善迴向菩提。法界眾生同階佛果。</p>
<lb n="0190c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0190c0401">次以塗香塗手。合掌如蓮。觀察本源。自性清
<lb n="0190c05" ed="T"/>淨。為諸客塵之所覆蔽。作此觀已。運心廣布。
<lb n="0190c06" ed="T"/>我與眾生亦同清淨。為令清淨故。誦此殊勝。
<lb n="0190c07" ed="T"/><note n="0190042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">浴澡＝澡浴【甲】</note><note n="0190042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">浴澡【大】，澡浴【甲】</note><app n="0190042"><lem wit="【大】">浴澡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">澡浴</rdg></app>真<note n="0190043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">言＋（曰）【甲】</note><note n="0190043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，言曰【甲】</note><app n="0190043"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">言曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0190c08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0190c0801" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>薩<note n="0190044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚩＝縛【甲】＊</note><note n="0190044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】＊，縛【甲】＊</note><app n="0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note><app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><g ref="#CB02122"/><note place="inline">詩律反</note>度唅</p>
<lb n="0190c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0190c0901">由三誦明故。身口意三業乃至遍法界一切
<lb n="0190c10" ed="T"/>悉清淨。</p>
<lb n="0190c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0190c1101">次結一切諸佛部心三昧耶印。</p>
<lb n="0190c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0190c1201">止觀十度內叉拳。禪智二度並申合。遍觀諸
<lb n="0190c13" ed="T"/>佛滿虛空。三誦真言頂上散。諸佛部心真言
<lb n="0190c14" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0190c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0190c1501" cb:type="dharani">唵<note n="0190045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【甲】</note><note n="0190045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0190045"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>爾曩爾迦<note place="inline">半字呼</note>娑<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note n="0190046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0190046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0190046"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0190c16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0190c1601">由結前印誦真言故。十方諸佛一切如來。承
<lb n="0190c17" ed="T"/>本誓願。皆悉運集。遍滿虛空。舒光照燭。加
<lb n="0190c18" ed="T"/>持行人。離諸障惱。三業清淨。速證菩提。</p>
<lb n="0190c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0190c1901">次結一切諸菩薩蓮華部心三昧耶印。</p>
<lb n="0190c20" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0190c2001"><l>准前結佛部心印</l><l><note n="0190047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">屈左＝次屈【甲】</note><note n="0190047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">屈左【大】，次屈【甲】</note><app n="0190047"><lem wit="【大】">屈左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">次屈</rdg></app>智度入掌中</l>
<lb n="0190c21" ed="T"/><l>禪度直竪或三招</l><l>運心憶<note n="0190048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">念＝仰【甲】</note><note n="0190048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念【大】，仰【甲】</note><app n="0190048"><lem wit="【大】">念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">仰</rdg></app>觀自在</l>
<lb n="0190c22" ed="T"/><l>一切微塵菩薩眾</l><l>持蓮眷屬滿空中</l>
<pb n="0191a" xml:id="T19.0949.0191a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0191a01" ed="T"/><l>至心三遍誦真言</l><l>方以印於頂右散</l></lg>
<lb n="0191a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a0201">蓮華部心真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0191a03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a0301" cb:type="dharani">唵阿<note place="inline">去</note>嚕力迦<note place="inline">半字呼</note>娑<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0191001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＋（引）細註【甲】＊</note><note n="0191001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賀【大】＊，賀(引)【甲】＊</note><app n="0191001"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0191a04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a0401">由結前印誦真言故。觀自在菩薩承本誓願。
<lb n="0191a05" ed="T"/>將<note n="0191002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">諸＋（持）【甲】</note><note n="0191002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸【大】，諸持【甲】</note><app n="0191002"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">諸持</rdg></app>蓮華眾無量菩薩。遍滿虛空。皆悉運
<lb n="0191a06" ed="T"/>集。放大光明。加持行者。令得清淨。所求滿
<lb n="0191a07" ed="T"/>足。離諸障難。疾證菩提。</p>
<lb n="0191a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a0801">次結一切金剛部心三昧耶印。</p>
<lb n="0191a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a0901">准前復結佛部心印。</p>
<lb n="0191a10" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0191a1001"><l>屈右禪度入掌中</l><l>智度直竪或三<note n="0191003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次下甲本有遍想金剛藏王眾一句</note>招</l>
<lb n="0191a11" ed="T"/><l>塵沙眷屬共圍繞</l><l>威光赫奕遍虛空</l>
<lb n="0191a12" ed="T"/><l>至誠三遍誦真言</l><l>方以印於頂左散</l></lg>
<lb n="0191a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a1301">金剛部心真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0191a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a1401" cb:type="dharani">唵<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日羅<note place="inline">二合</note>地力<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<note place="inline">半字呼</note>娑縛<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<app type="star" corresp="#0190046"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0191a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a1501">由結前印誦真言故。十方一切金剛手等承
<lb n="0191a16" ed="T"/>本願因。如雲而集。現大威德。加持行人。除障
<lb n="0191a17" ed="T"/>摧魔。自在無礙。疾成悉地。速至菩提。</p>
<lb n="0191a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a1801">次結金剛甲冑護身印。</p>
<lb n="0191a19" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0191a1901"><l>止觀羽作金剛拳</l><l>禪智橫屈於掌內</l>
<lb n="0191a20" ed="T"/><l>進力如鉤慣甲勢</l><l>加持心額二肩喉</l>
<lb n="0191a21" ed="T"/><l>至<note n="0191004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心＝誠【甲】</note><note n="0191004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心【大】，誠【甲】</note><app n="0191004"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">誠</rdg></app>三遍誦真言</l><l>印身五處頂上散</l></lg>
<lb n="0191a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a2201">甲冑護身真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0191a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a2301" cb:type="dharani">唵<note n="0191005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB03514"/>＝部【甲】</note><note n="0191005" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><g ref="#CB03514"/>【大】，部【甲】</note><app n="0191005"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB03514"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">部</rdg></app>入<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>攞<note place="inline">二合</note>𤙖</p>
<lb n="0191a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191a2401">由結甲印誦真言故。加持五處。成大護身。即
<lb n="0191a25" ed="T"/>同金剛堅固之體。金剛藏王承本願力。領諸
<lb n="0191a26" ed="T"/>眷屬。數如塵沙無量金剛圍遶侍從。光明熾
<lb n="0191a27" ed="T"/>盛。現忿怒形。加持行人。威德自在。辟除作
<lb n="0191a28" ed="T"/>障。摧壞諸魔。小則能護一身。大則護持國界。
<lb n="0191a29" ed="T"/>一切災厄。水火刀兵。毒藥<note n="0191006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蠱＝毒虫【甲】</note><note n="0191006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蠱【大】，毒虫【甲】</note><app n="0191006"><lem wit="【大】">蠱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">毒虫</rdg></app>虎狼猛獸。皆
<pb n="0191b" xml:id="T19.0949.0191b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0191b01" ed="T"/>悉遠離不敢視之。毘那藥迦自然怖走。永無
<lb n="0191b02" ed="T"/>惱害。疾證菩提。</p>
<lb n="0191b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191b0301">次結辨<note n="0191007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">事＋（辟除）【甲】</note><note n="0191007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">事【大】，事辟除【甲】</note><app n="0191007"><lem wit="【大】">事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">事辟除</rdg></app>印。</p>
<lb n="0191b04" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0191b0401"><l>止觀二羽內叉拳</l><l>禪智雙屈入掌中</l>
<lb n="0191b05" ed="T"/><l>然申忍願頭相跓</l><l>頂上三旋成結護</l>
<lb n="0191b06" ed="T"/><l>左轉三匝是辟除</l><l>隨心所到作方隅</l>
<lb n="0191b07" ed="T"/><l>破法能成一切事</l></lg>
<lb n="0191b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191b0801"><note n="0191b0801" resp="CBETA" type="add">辦【CB】，辨【大】</note><app n="0191b0801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">辦<note type="cf1">F28n1071_p0003b08</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">辨</rdg></app>事佛頂真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0191b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191b0901" cb:type="dharani">曩莫三<note place="inline">去</note>漫多母馱南<note place="inline">引</note>唵拏嚕唵<note place="inline">二合</note>滿馱娑
<lb n="0191b10" ed="T"/>嚩<note place="inline">二合</note><app type="star" corresp="#0191001"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0191b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191b1101">由結前印及誦真言。悉能辟除及結護界。是
<lb n="0191b12" ed="T"/>名諸佛警悟聖心。能破他法。壞滅魔羅。天龍
<lb n="0191b13" ed="T"/>八部。羅剎藥叉。毘那夜迦。忙怖奔走。由結此
<lb n="0191b14" ed="T"/>印。世出世間一切事業速能成<note n="0191b1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">辦【CB】，辨【大】</note><app n="0191b1401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA">辦</lem><rdg wit="【大】">辨</rdg></app>。自在無礙。
<lb n="0191b15" ed="T"/>悉地現前。</p>
<lb n="0191b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191b1601">次結奉獻閼伽印。</p>
<lb n="0191b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191b1701">二羽仰掌<note n="0191008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捨＝捧【甲】</note><note n="0191008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捨【大】，捧【甲】</note><app n="0191008"><lem wit="【大】">捨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">捧</rdg></app>器形。</p>
<lb n="0191b18" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0191b1801"><l>進力屈於忍願傍</l><l>禪智曲補於進力</l>
<lb n="0191b19" ed="T"/><l>捧器三旋當額上</l><l>想浴聖眾淨如蓮</l></lg>
<lb n="0191b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191b2001">閼伽浴聖真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0191b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191b2101" cb:type="dharani">曩麼三<note place="inline">去</note>滿多母馱南<note place="inline">引</note>誐誐曩糝魔沙麼娑
<lb n="0191b22" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0191b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191b2301">由結此印誦真言奉獻閼伽浴聖故。表<note n="0191009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">修＝滌【甲】</note><note n="0191009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">修【大】，滌【甲】</note><app n="0191009"><lem wit="【大】">修</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">滌</rdg></app>行
<lb n="0191b24" ed="T"/>人無始垢業蕩除清淨。如妙蓮華。當來果獲
<lb n="0191b25" ed="T"/>得無染智。</p>
<lb n="0191b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191b2601">次結虛空普供印。</p>
<lb n="0191b27" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0191b2701"><l>二羽合掌交初分</l><l>右押左縛如金剛</l>
<lb n="0191b28" ed="T"/><l>想成真實微妙供</l><l>無量雲海奉聖眾</l>
<lb n="0191b29" ed="T"/><l>供養一切諸如來</l><l>後說四句妙伽他</l>
<pb n="0191c" xml:id="T19.0949.0191c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0191c01" ed="T"/><l>五誦真言頂上散</l></lg><p xml:id="pT19p0191c0108" rend="inline">虛空大明真言曰</p>
<lb n="0191c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191c0201" cb:type="dharani">曩莫三滿多沒馱南<note place="inline">引</note>薩<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>他<app type="star" corresp="#0190046"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>欠<note n="0191010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">盟＝<g ref="#CB14002"/>【甲】</note><note n="0191010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盟【大】，<g ref="#CB14002"/>【甲】</note><app n="0191010"><lem wit="【大】">盟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><g ref="#CB14002"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0191c03" ed="T"/>娜孽帝薩頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉呬𤚥誐誐曩劍娑<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<anchor xml:id="fxT19p0191c04"/>引</note>
<lb n="0191c04" ed="T"/>賀</p>
<lb n="0191c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191c0501">由結此印誦真言故。以不思議力。從<note n="0191011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印流出乃至明照一切三百四十字甲本欠</note><note n="0191011" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->（印流出…明照一切）三百四十字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note>印流出
<lb n="0191c06" ed="T"/>一切供養。無量天眾各持天寶器。盛諸妙供
<lb n="0191c07" ed="T"/>養。塞滿虛空所謂塗香燒燈。飲食衣服。幢蓋
<lb n="0191c08" ed="T"/>瓔珞。奉獻如來誦一遍故。流出塗香。當來獲
<lb n="0191c09" ed="T"/>得戒品塗香。誦二遍故。流出焚香。當來獲得
<lb n="0191c10" ed="T"/>定芬馥。誦三遍故。流出花鬘。當來獲得離染
<lb n="0191c11" ed="T"/>妙蓮。誦四遍故。流出寶食。當來獲得法喜禪
<lb n="0191c12" ed="T"/>悅。誦五遍故。流出寶燈。當來獲得如來五眼。
<lb n="0191c13" ed="T"/>當得如上諸功德波羅蜜門皆具足。復以心
<lb n="0191c14" ed="T"/>遍法界。以誠實言誦妙伽他。而說偈言。</p>
<lb n="0191c15" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0191c1501"><l>以我功德力</l><l>如來加持力</l>
<lb n="0191c16" ed="T"/><l>及以法界力</l><l>普供養而住</l></lg>
<lb n="0191c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191c1701">次以梵讚歌詠。本尊相好金身殊勝功德。</p>
<lb n="0191c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191c1801" cb:type="dharani">麼禰史膩薩嚩若誐<note place="inline">一</note>地帶史膩拽捨枲嚩<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0191c19" ed="T"/>合</note>𩕳<note place="inline">二</note>步嘌步晚禰迦滿馱<note place="inline">三</note>三麼娑多<note place="inline">二合</note>尾
<lb n="0191c20" ed="T"/>儞也<note place="inline">二合</note>地跛<note place="inline">四</note>訖羅<note place="inline">二合</note>麼哩𩕳曩謨窣覩<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0191c21" ed="T"/>合</note>帝怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>哆哩左訖羅<note place="inline">二合</note>嚩<note place="inline">轉舌</note>底𩕳<note place="inline">六</note></p>
<lb n="0191c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191c2201">由讚佛三身。六根諸功德。八萬四千種。殊勝
<lb n="0191c23" ed="T"/>不思議。承斯歌詠因。當來獲妙果。福聚海無
<lb n="0191c24" ed="T"/>量。等同奇特尊。</p>
<lb n="0191c25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191c2501">次結佛眼大明印。</p>
<lb n="0191c26" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0191c2601"><l>止觀虛合未開敷</l><l>禪智雙屈在掌中</l>
<lb n="0191c27" ed="T"/><l>進力各押忍願背</l><l>如眼開明照一切</l>
<lb n="0191c28" ed="T"/><l>安<note n="0191012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眉＝肩【甲】</note><note n="0191012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眉【大】，肩【甲】</note><app n="0191012"><lem wit="【大】">眉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">肩</rdg></app>心額二肩喉</l><l>起大悲愍怖畏除</l></lg>
<lb n="0191c29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0191c2901">隨誦真言頂上散。</p>
<pb n="0192a" xml:id="T19.0949.0192a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0192a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192a0101">佛眼大明母真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0192a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192a0201" cb:type="dharani">曩莫薩<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>怛他<note place="inline">去引</note>蘗帝毘庾<note place="inline"><note n="0192001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（二合）＋引【甲】</note><note n="0192001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，二合引【甲】</note><app n="0192001"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二合引</rdg></app>一</note>囉褐<note n="0192002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合二〕－【甲】</note><note n="0192002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合二【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0192002"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0192a03" ed="T"/>毘藥<note place="inline">二<note n="0192003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（二）【甲】</note><note n="0192003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合【大】，合二【甲】</note><app n="0192003"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合二</rdg></app></note>三藐三沒弟毘藥<note place="inline">二合三</note>唵<note place="inline">四</note>嚕嚕窣
<lb n="0192a04" ed="T"/><note n="0192004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">普嚕二合＝普二合嚕五【甲】</note><note n="0192004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">普嚕二合【大】，普二合嚕五【甲】</note><app n="0192004"><lem wit="【大】">普嚕<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">普二合嚕五</rdg></app>入<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>攞底<note place="inline">丁以反</note>瑟姹<note place="inline">二合六</note>悉馱路<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0192a05" ed="T"/>左𩕳薩<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0192005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𡃤＝喇【甲】</note><note n="0192005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𡃤【大】，喇【甲】</note><app n="0192005"><lem wit="【大】">𡃤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">喇</rdg></app>他<note place="inline">二合去聲呼</note>娑<note place="inline">去</note>馱𩕳<note place="inline">八</note>娑<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0192a06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0192a07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192a0701">此名一切佛眼大明。能息可畏難調伏者。為
<lb n="0192a08" ed="T"/>欲成就世間出世間一切佛頂大輪王法一切
<lb n="0192a09" ed="T"/>事位滅諸諍論。亦是一切諸佛種族母。復是
<lb n="0192a10" ed="T"/>一切諸大菩薩生養母。為說頂輪真言威德
<lb n="0192a11" ed="T"/>奇特。諸大菩薩皆<note n="0192006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">失本心乃至證悉地三百十三字甲本欠</note><note n="0192006" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->失本心乃至證悉地三百十三字甲本欠</note>失本心。諸天龍神威力滅
<lb n="0192a12" ed="T"/>沒。凡誦一字佛頂明。先須誦佛眼明。念誦畢
<lb n="0192a13" ed="T"/>已。亦誦七遍。眾聖歡喜安樂有情。</p>
<lb n="0192a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192a1401">次結一字根本印。</p>
<lb n="0192a15" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0192a1501"><l>止觀密縛內叉拳</l><l>由慼忍願如劍形</l>
<lb n="0192a16" ed="T"/><l>禪智進力甲柱跓</l><l>是名金剛佛頂印</l>
<lb n="0192a17" ed="T"/><l>想身威德同本尊</l><l>流光晃曜遍十方</l></lg>
<lb n="0192a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192a1801">印身五處頂上散。</p>
<lb n="0192a19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192a1901">金輪頂王真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0192a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192a2001" cb:type="dharani">曩謨三漫多<note place="inline">一</note>母馱南<note place="inline">二</note>唵𤙖<g ref="#CB03514"/>𡄦<note place="inline">二合彈舌重呼</note>𤙖</p>
<lb n="0192a21" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0192a2101"><l>此是摩訶印</l><l>所謂如來頂</l>
<lb n="0192a22" ed="T"/><l>由斯結誦故</l><l>即同於世尊</l>
<lb n="0192a23" ed="T"/><l>演說頂輪明</l><l>三千六反動</l>
<lb n="0192a24" ed="T"/><l>山河皆勇沸</l><l>大火遍魔宮</l>
<lb n="0192a25" ed="T"/><l>惶怖盡歸依</l><l>地獄眾苦息</l>
<lb n="0192a26" ed="T"/><l>菩薩龍天眾</l><l>畏仰如佛身</l></lg>
<lb n="0192a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192a2701">次結大慈普護印。</p>
<lb n="0192a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192a2801">十度相叉作月形　禪智檀惠相著　印心額
<pb n="0192b" xml:id="T19.0949.0192b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0192b01" ed="T"/>喉頂上散</p>
<lb n="0192b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192b0201">慈護真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0192b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192b0301" cb:type="dharani">唵沒馱昧怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>嚩<note n="0192b0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">日【CB】，曰【大】</note><app n="0192b0301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>洛乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>憾</p>
<lb n="0192b04" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0192b0401"><l>結印誦明除怖畏</l><l>起大悲心遍一切</l>
<lb n="0192b05" ed="T"/><l>所有怨敵惡相淩</l><l>願彼皆當大安樂</l>
<lb n="0192b06" ed="T"/><l>由此三誦悲護故</l><l>毒害之心自覺悟</l>
<lb n="0192b07" ed="T"/><l>深生悔過向菩提</l><l>歡喜敬仰前人所</l>
<lb n="0192b08" ed="T"/><l>初後若常誦此明</l><l>惶怖眾生得安慰</l>
<lb n="0192b09" ed="T"/><l>護大利益殊勝事</l><l>速滿諸願證悉地</l></lg>
<lb n="0192b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192b1001">次結淨珠印。</p>
<lb n="0192b11" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0192b1101"><l>盤珠於掌內</l><l>如蓮未開形<note n="0192007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲本有進力屈上節一句</note><note n="0192007" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: a-->甲本有進力屈上節一句</note></l>
<lb n="0192b12" ed="T"/><l>捧合於心上</l><l>三七遍加持</l>
<lb n="0192b13" ed="T"/><l>頂戴慇重心</l><l>如法而供養</l></lg>
<lb n="0192b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192b1401">淨珠真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0192b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192b1501" cb:type="dharani">唵阿<note n="0192008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𠺶<g ref="#CB03514"/>＝納部【甲】</note><note n="0192008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𠺶<g ref="#CB03514"/>【大】，納部【甲】</note><app n="0192008"><lem wit="【大】">𠺶<g ref="#CB03514"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">納部</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<anchor xml:id="fxT19p0192b01"/>引</note>帝𠳿惹曳<note place="inline">而異反</note>悉地<note place="inline">引</note>悉馱<note n="0192009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𡃤二合＝賴【甲】</note><note n="0192009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𡃤二合【大】，賴【甲】</note><app n="0192009"><lem wit="【大】">𡃤
<lb n="0192b16" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賴</rdg></app>剃娑嚩<note place="inline">二合<anchor xml:id="fxT19p0192b02"/><anchor xml:id="fxT19p0192b03"/>引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0192b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192b1701">次結持數印。</p>
<lb n="0192b18" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0192b1801"><l>二羽半金剛</l><l>禪智捻戒方</l>
<lb n="0192b19" ed="T"/><l>進力忍願後<note place="inline">屈不相著</note></l><l>七遍持<note n="0192010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">數＝珠【甲】</note><note n="0192010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">數【大】，珠【甲】</note><app n="0192010"><lem wit="【大】">數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">珠</rdg></app>明</l></lg>
<lb n="0192b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192b2001">然後而念誦。</p>
<lb n="0192b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192b2101">持珠真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0192b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192b2201" cb:type="dharani">曩莫婆誐<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>帝蘇悉地娑馱也娑馱也娑馱
<lb n="0192b23" ed="T"/>囉剃娑<app type="star" corresp="#0190044"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<anchor xml:id="fxT19p0192b06"/>引</note><app type="star" corresp="#0191001"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0192b24" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0192b2401"><l>先當淨三業</l><l>加法而念誦</l>
<lb n="0192b25" ed="T"/><l>一心莫散亂</l><l><note n="0192011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">注＝住【甲】</note><note n="0192011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">注【大】，住【甲】</note><app n="0192011"><lem wit="【大】">注</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">住</rdg></app>想於本尊</l>
<lb n="0192b26" ed="T"/><l>字句分明呼</l><l>不緩亦不急</l>
<lb n="0192b27" ed="T"/><l>勿生懈怠意</l><l><note n="0192012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聲咳及頻申＝<g ref="#CB14024"/>吹及𩓙呻【甲】</note><note n="0192012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聲咳及頻申【大】，<g ref="#CB14024"/>吹及𩓙呻【甲】</note><app n="0192012"><lem wit="【大】">聲咳及頻申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><g ref="#CB14024"/>吹及𩓙呻</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0192b28" ed="T"/><l>雜染縱惛沈</l><l>如是諸過咎</l>
<lb n="0192b29" ed="T"/><l>少分生<note n="0192013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">忘＝妄【明】</note><note n="0192013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忘【大】，妄【明】</note><app n="0192013"><lem wit="【大】">忘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">妄</rdg></app>緣</l><l>皆不得成就</l>
<pb n="0192c" xml:id="T19.0949.0192c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0192c01" ed="T"/><l>念誦課數畢</l><l>持珠安舊處</l>
<lb n="0192c02" ed="T"/><l>方入三昧耶</l><l><note n="0192014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當＝常【甲】</note><note n="0192014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當【大】，常【甲】</note><app n="0192014"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">常</rdg></app>住本尊觀</l>
<lb n="0192c03" ed="T"/><l>食頃從定出</l><l>却結根本印</l>
<lb n="0192c04" ed="T"/><l>次結佛眼明</l><l>歌詠音讚歎</l>
<lb n="0192c05" ed="T"/><l>普供閼伽已</l><l>辟除左解散</l>
<lb n="0192c06" ed="T"/><l>三部重護身</l><l>最後慈護印</l>
<lb n="0192c07" ed="T"/><l>禮悔依前儀</l><l>讀誦大乘典</l>
<lb n="0192c08" ed="T"/><l>隨意任經行</l><l>常時莫間斷</l></lg>
<lb n="0192c09" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>頂輪王<note n="0192015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">要略一卷＝念誦要略儀軌【甲】</note><note n="0192015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">要略一卷【大】，念誦要略儀軌【甲】</note><app n="0192015"><lem wit="【大】">要略一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">念誦要略儀軌</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0192c10" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><head><note n="0192016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以下甲本無之，此行原本朱書</note>奇特最勝金輪佛頂念誦儀軌法要</head>
<lb n="0192c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192c1101">若不能誦向前大佛眼真言誦此心真言亦得
<lb n="0192c12" ed="T"/><note n="0192017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此行原本朱書</note>佛眼小呪也。</p>
<lb n="0192c13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192c1301" cb:type="dharani"><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><space quantity="0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">曩</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><space quantity="0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">莫</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><space quantity="0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">三</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><space quantity="0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">滿</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><space quantity="0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">多</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><space quantity="0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">沒</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><space quantity="0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>馱</cb:zi><cb:sg>引</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><space quantity="0"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>喃</cb:zi><cb:sg>引</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><note n="0192018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此陀羅尼梵字原本朱書</note><g ref="#SD-DA42"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">唵</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E3AD"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">沒</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-D9FA"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>馱</cb:zi><cb:sg>引</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A652"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">路</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A47C"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">左</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5AF"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>𩕳</cb:zi><cb:sg>引</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-B065"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>娑嚩</cb:zi><cb:sg>二合引</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0192c14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0192c15" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A6A9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">賀</cb:t></cb:tt></p></cb:div>
<lb n="0192c16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0192c17" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pT19p0192c1701" rend="margin-left:12em"><note n="0192019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">教舜以下原本朱書</note><cb:tt rend="inline"><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">教舜</cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E0EE"/></cb:t></cb:tt></p>
<lb n="0192c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192c1801" rend="margin-left:12em">二交了</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0192c19" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><head>水壇法</head>
<lb n="0192c20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0192c2001">取新淨牛糞。不食糟豆特。犢子糞最第一。不
<lb n="0192c21" ed="T"/>得直用其生牛糞。取新瓦鑵以汲淨水。不用
<lb n="0192c22" ed="T"/>殘水。寫淨<g ref="#CB03546"/>中。以糞和水。攪去其滓。著檀香
<lb n="0192c23" ed="T"/>末。取一柳枝。以右手執。左手執金剛杵及其
<lb n="0192c24" ed="T"/>數珠。東坐誦佛頂心呪。柳枝攪水。呪一百八
<lb n="0192c25" ed="T"/>遍。持呪水器。入道場中。從東北角捕其香水。
<lb n="0192c26" ed="T"/>以右手摩地。隨日轉摩。隨摩隨乾。勿令停水。
<lb n="0192c27" ed="T"/>道場內地一編摩訖。乃至道場水四邊摩。各
<lb n="0192c28" ed="T"/>一步地四角竪標結繩為界。此則名為佛頂
<lb n="0192c29" ed="T"/>三昧陀羅尼結界之地。如一編摩。第二第三
<lb n="0192c30" ed="T"/>亦如是摩。摩地不得用殘香水。日日別取新
<pb n="0193a" xml:id="T19.0949.0193a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0193a01" ed="T"/>淨牛糞。准前作用。作此水者。則名佛頂三昧
<lb n="0193a02" ed="T"/>陀羅尼八功德水壇地乾竟。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0193a03" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pT19p0193a0301">　　　　　　　　　　　　　二校了</p></cb:div></cb:div>
